Title: RogueTS
Description: RogueTS is a Roguelike engine written in TypeScript. It features randomly generated maps, basic lighting effects, collision detection and additional stub code.
HomeWiki: RogueTS is a TypeScript port of F*Rogue which is a Rogue like engine written I originally wrote in ActionScript. The F*Rogue engine features randomly generated maps, basic lighting effects, collision detection and stub code for building an inventory system. I am slowly porting over the rest of F*Rogue to RogueTS so stay tuned.
